data.description: This beautiful 2 story home is located in the desirable Rosewood community. Minutes from shopping and restaurants, It features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and an office that could double as a 4th bedroom. There is a large bonus room, a formal dining area, and large living room with hardwood floors. Relax on the wrap around front porch that's big enough for the whole family, or retreat to your master suite and relax by your private fireplace. Enjoy the 2 car garage, concrete drive, attached storage room/workshop. The home is spacious with over 2800 sq ft it has plenty of room for a growing family. It's a must see.
